briefdescription.para: Macro to configure the External High Speed oscillator (HSE) Predivision factor for PLL.

simplesect.para: Predivision factor can not be changed if PLL is used as system clock In this case, you have to select another source of the system clock, disable the PLL and then change the HSE predivision factor.

parameterdescription.para: specifies the division value applied to HSE. This parameter must be a number between RCC_HSE_PREDIV_DIV1 and RCC_HSE_PREDIV_DIV2.

briefdescription.para: Macro to get prediv1 factor for PLL.
Macro to configure the ADCx clock (x=1 to 3 depending on devices).

parameterdescription.para:
specifies the ADC clock source. This parameter can be one of the following values:
RCC_ADCPCLK2_DIV2 PCLK2 clock divided by 2 selected as ADC clock
RCC_ADCPCLK2_DIV4 PCLK2 clock divided by 4 selected as ADC clock
RCC_ADCPCLK2_DIV6 PCLK2 clock divided by 6 selected as ADC clock
RCC_ADCPCLK2_DIV8 PCLK2 clock divided by 8 selected as ADC clock

briefdescription.para: Macro to get the ADC clock (ADCxCLK, x=1 to 3 depending on devices).

parameterdescription.para:
clock source can be one of the following values:
RCC_ADCPCLK2_DIV2 PCLK2 clock divided by 2 selected as ADC clock
RCC_ADCPCLK2_DIV4 PCLK2 clock divided by 4 selected as ADC clock
RCC_ADCPCLK2_DIV6 PCLK2 clock divided by 6 selected as ADC clock
RCC_ADCPCLK2_DIV8 PCLK2 clock divided by 8 selected as ADC clock
